<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Auto-Record - Panel del Checador</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/img/google.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800">

    <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 via-blue-700 to-sky-500 text-white shadow-lg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img src="/img/LogoProyecto.jpeg" alt="Logo Auto-Record" class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-white shadow-md">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide">Auto-Record</h1>
                <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">Control inteligente para rutas y unidades</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm md:text-base font-medium">
            <a href="/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white/15 hover:bg-white/25 transition">Inicio</a>
            <a href="/funciones" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Funciones</a>
            <a href="/descargas" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Descargas</a>
            <a href="/nosotros" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Nosotros</a>
            <a href="/informacion" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/15 transition">Información</a>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <section class="mb-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between gap-6">
                <div>
                    <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
                        Módulo de supervisión y control
                    </span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-3">Panel del Checador</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                        Bienvenido(a), <strong class="text-blue-800"><%= user.name %></strong>. Desde este panel puedes registrar vueltas, supervisar choferes en servicio y mantener el control diario de las rutas activas.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-blue-100 p-5 min-w-[260px]">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">Rol activo</p>
                    <p class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800">Checador</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Gestión de entradas, salidas y seguimiento operativo en tiempo real.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-5 mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 shadow-md p-6">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Choferes activos</p>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-700">12</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Choferes actualmente en operación.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 shadow-md p-6">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Unidades en ruta</p>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-700">10</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Unidades activas dentro del servicio.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 shadow-md p-6">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Incidencias reportadas</p>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-700">2</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Eventos o incidencias registradas hoy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-700 to-sky-500 text-white rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-blue-100 mb-2">Acción rápida</p>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Reporte diario</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">Consulta el resumen general de la jornada.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="mt-5 inline-block bg-white text-blue-700 font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
                    Ver reporte
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">📝</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800">Registro de Vuelta</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Captura horarios y asignaciones del servicio</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <form class="space-y-5">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Unidad asignada</label>
                            <select class="w-full rounded-xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400">
                                <option>Seleccionar</option>
                                <option>TP-482</option>
                                <option>TP-501</option>
                                <option>TP-399</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Nombre del chofer</label>
                            <select class="w-full rounded-xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400">
                                <option>Selecciona</option>
                                <option>Oliver Sanchez</option>
                                <option>Aranza Garrido</option>
                                <option>Jeysi Damari</option>
                                <option>Laura Sanchez</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Hora de salida</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="00:00" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400">
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Hora de llegada</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="00:00" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-blue-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <button type="button" class="w-full bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-md transition">
                            Guardar registro
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 p-8">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Choferes activos hoy</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500">Consulta el estado actual de operación de cada chofer.</p>
                        </div>

                        <button type="button" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-semibold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl transition">
                            Generar reporte
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                        <table class="w-full min-w-[700px] text-left border-collapse">
                            <thead>
                                <tr class="bg-blue-50 text-slate-700">
                                    <th class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">Nombre</th>
                                    <th class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">Ruta asignada</th>
                                    <th class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">Entrada</th>
                                    <th class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">Salida</th>
                                    <th class="px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">Estado</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
                                <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50">
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 font-medium text-slate-800">Carlos Méndez</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">Ruta 5 - Centro</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">06:00</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">-</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4">
                                        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">
                                            En ruta
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>

                                <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50">
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 font-medium text-slate-800">Ana Ramírez</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">Ruta 3 - Sur</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">06:15</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">14:00</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4">
                                        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">
                                            Finalizado
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>

                                <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50">
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 font-medium text-slate-800">José Gutiérrez</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">Ruta 7 - Norte</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">-</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">-</td>
                                    <td class="px-4 py-4">
                                        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">
                                            Sin registrar
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Control operativo en tiempo real</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed mb-5">
                        Mantén una supervisión más precisa sobre salidas, llegadas y estado de las unidades para mejorar la coordinación del servicio y reducir errores en el registro manual.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-6">
                        <a href="/auth/logout"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-white text-blue-800 font-semibold shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
                            Cerrar sesión
                        </a>

                        <a href="/"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/30 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition">
                            Ir al inicio
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 mt-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 text-center text-sm">
            TechHive Labs 2025 • Gestión inteligente de transporte público
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>